93-73a3b7649973\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAyMDNfMjEy/MDAxNzM4NTY2ODA4NTYw.ptKFqlmGwBuXdnZOeMyPyPubq7_DHrToGXUkyP7hAogg.MUXkF2IEZovNxWN2Y_hrFxtNHTv7Fw7H5iB4V99e1akg.JPEG/%EA%B8%B0%ED%83%80_1.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1411\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1058\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAyMDNfMjEy/MDAxNzM4NTY2ODA4NTYw.ptKFqlmGwBuXdnZOeMyPyPubq7_DHrToGXUkyP7hAogg.MUXkF2IEZovNxWN2Y_hrFxtNHTv7Fw7H5iB4V99e1akg.JPEG/%EA%B8%B0%ED%83%80_1.jpg?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-c9088830-2407-4b0d-a515-354b43ad5569\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAyMDNfMTY1/MDAxNzM4NTY2ODA4NjAy.lnYc6qF84yTKvyuD5DoJN6a8OMwQRCvD8uNdC1cdxF8g.Y9Vyl0v6S5PXFkfyBz56ErFD7Z1fWaDWL1RaiRePuP8g.JPEG/%ED%8E%84_3.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1411\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1058\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAyMDNfMTY1/MDAxNzM4NTY2ODA4NjAy.lnYc6qF84yTKvyuD5DoJN6a8OMwQRCvD8uNdC1cdxF8g.Y9Vyl0v6S5PXFkfyBz56ErFD7Z1fWaDWL1RaiRePuP8g.JPEG/%ED%8E%84_3.jpg?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d4e172f0-dd95-4ba7-91b0-5daa2eab3696\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9cd48900-ac04-45bc-8b7d-9c3781093b9f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1577f31b-77a6-41b8-aecc-8053ea6a1331\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4022366b-85ad-48a5-a3e8-a372fb6af98a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>크라프트지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c542344f-ecbe-4758-bd57-6b724ae11f12\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b610327c-f3b4-4046-a1c0-5a6aaaf36ebb\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">천연 크라프트 펄프를 사용한 친환경 제품입니다. FSC 무검출 인증 제품으로 음식이나 식품 류 포장재로도 사용이 가능하며 가성비 대비 단가적인 측면에서도 이점이 있는 종이입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dd0f9d34-88b4-494f-9d8b-ad782312ad30\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8c684dc5-d0f0-4fee-b9c3-75462b2c337a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">색상은 갈색을 띠며 연한 갈색이나 기타 생산하는 지업사에 따라 약간의 색상 차가 발생할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f87a91a3-8d99-493a-b112-06784e8c2807\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9da80211-f0d1-4903-9936-b6a4ede3a68d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">또한 161g ~ 337 g까지 다양한 두께로 생산되므로 패키지나 쇼핑백용으로 적합합니다. 다만 더 튼튼한 포장지를 위해 합지를 하여 제작되는 경우가 많습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-271d2d79-4c99-4ecf-bb0f-87dcee10baab\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d2f2109e-a6b2-4976-a039-aaf362b3d989\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6247832b-3c51-4b49-8436-e7102602e190\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b657e94c-c819-40e4-bfa0-00f20a004e09\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\": \"SE-b657e94c-c819-40e4-bfa0-00f20a004e09\", \"link\": \"https://www.samwhapaper.com/product/samwhapaper/premium/38\"}' data-linktype=\"text\" href=\"https://www.samwhapaper.com/product/samwhapaper/premium/38\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.samwhapaper.com/product/samwhapaper/premium/38</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> \n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-624e20e9-4d6b-47c6-92a2-63e35f0d03f7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:450px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-624e20e9-4d6b-47c6-92a2-63e35f0d03f7\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAyMDNfOTYg/MDAxNzM4NTY3NzM4ODQ3.eAwPc0SNMVHRg17LsHiefLrxw6quVRgkmdjlpQJCFdYg.z3DQue_PTi3OBlwAeFcaFB6f1t1jWM_oxuzGxBj21Bgg.PNG/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"450\", \"originalHeight\" : \"450\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAyMDNfOTYg/MDAxNzM4NTY3NzM4ODQ3.eAwPc0SNMVHRg17LsHiefLrxw6quVRgkmdjlpQJCFdYg.z3DQue_PTi3OBlwAeFcaFB6f1t1jWM_oxuzGxBj21Bgg.PNG/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a5740cde-8f9a-4b3f-94ec-dbef8a0a671a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-70d6add7-beaf-49be-9864-63e17dd38923\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c578662e-7dc7-4e9b-91fb-1ca7c0de821a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>크라프트 종이의</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-cc3b9fee-9acc-4317-8684-33fe69009176\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> 특징은 저렴하면서 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7e36f597-808f-4b53-aa78-c2b71e1ce091\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>친환경으로 갈색의 자연스러운 맛</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-49be28d0-001e-463f-a5cb-0d34ff975706\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">을 느낄 수 있는 종이입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b04b573c-4f0a-46cf-a119-99bd19f47265\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-144b2683-c70a-45a6-b8f0-d09cd8bedc6a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c6e5f8a0-8ca7-4f0d-ae77-d7e4f12c5a8e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5c5d0fec-b502-426a-95de-ba2073fd70f2\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">· 색상 : 갈색 / 후면 갈색</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-660b0dff-77ad-49ff-b24b-72fab0fadc9c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-bc94748a-c5ef-4798-8227-1a76fb79ecc7\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">· 평량 : 161g, 175g, 200g, 250g, 300g, 337g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-16c52058-b3a9-47b3-bbfb-dce2990dbe4b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-29b46c60-4cb3-4178-8626-0c531c1df2d1\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">· 용도 : 식품 가공식품, 팬시, 쇼핑백 등</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-02c5f8b7-6ab5-4734-8a08-445344fc85f7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0c9036a9-6c76-4cab-adcf-d1b6c4b2ac37\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ef53d2c0-9478-4667-9103-b49c0eecd417\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c5d2a16a-e906-4597-b7a2-c84d856d8f48\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>· 특징 : 이 종이는 친환경을 우선합니다. 또한 자연스러운 맛이 있는 종이지만 바탕이 흰색이 아닌 갈색이므로 인쇄 시 색상 조합을 잘 표현해야 흐리거나 잘 보이지 않는 사고가 나지 않습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-67d25134-8712-478f-99e1-236c52fec8a7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-t